{"tid":1747130,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(重溫2015年區選）千其唔好支持黎明投票","createTime":"2019-11-23T05:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T13:02:08.000Z","uid":69159,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ef13b851d5995e774900ba914610e01b93e578ad","tid":1747130,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:38:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20151123/mobile/bkn-20151123034149636-1123_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20151123%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20151123034149636-1123_00822_001.html&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=fadd4ec0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20151123/mobile/bkn-20151123034149636-1123_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2015年區議會選舉點票工作如火如荼，葵青石籬南卻爆出選票失蹤疑雲。有知情人士報稱，投票總數為7千多，但點票後發現只有6千多張選票，1千票不翼而飛，其後封箱尋求法律意見。惟亦有指在封箱後，工作人員才發現全日只發出了6千多張選票，7千多票純屬誤報。該區有兩名候選人，分別是民主黨的梁國華及新民黨的吳家超。<br />\n<br />\n黎明投票絕對係集中票源嘅方法<br />\n最佳投票時間係旅遊巴送老人去投票<br />\n將我地嘅票混入票箱<br />\n<br />\n黎明投票只要整唔見個票箱就解決左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1700a68205f59ca0d41d3d7826e2ec574d430e8","tid":1747130,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:17:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e5e337317b98261cd18e433df300ad29fbe5c8b","tid":1747130,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:19:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5cf315bd5b03d16f4d9baab3ab86a6ab522ae9fb","tid":1747130,"uid":277590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:24:08.000Z","msg":"有道理<br />\n如該屋企望到票站<br />\n可以等班老人家岀現再衝去排<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無得投票嘅同學仔聽日有咩可以做？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747161</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"63567f236e2d1f98a653a55b46dd0272bfc3eb8d","tid":1747130,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re